ArcTouch Code Challenge

Libraries:
- com.neenbedankt.gradle.plugins:android-apt:1.8 -> used for Android Annotations;
- io.realm:realm-gradle-plugin:1.1.1' -> used for mobile database;
- com.squareup.retrofit:retrofit:2.0.0-beta2 -> used for REST service;
- com.github.bumptech.glide:glide:3.7.0' -> used for handling images;
- com.github.pwittchen:infinitescroll:0.0.1'-> used for infinite scroll in RecyclerView;
